The Department of States Services has just released Chido Onumah. A source close to Onumah confirmed this, saying; "DSS spokesperson, Peter Afunaya, just confirmed to me now and I spoke to Chido also." Onumah was arrested by the DSS at the Nnamdi Azikwe International Airport, Abuja, upon arriving the country from a trip abroad. 



